Enum TypeCellFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TypeCellFactory>
      • org.knime.base.node.preproc.constantvalue.TypeCellFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TypeCellFactory>

    enum TypeCellFactory
extends Enum<TypeCellFactory>
    A TypeCellFactory creates for a string and an optional additional parameter a new cell.
    Author:
    Marcel Hanser

    • Enum Constant Summary
